Invocation Name: smell my fart
des: Smell My Fart is a comedic skill designed for humor and entertainment. Every day, users can interact with Alexa to receive a funny and sarcastic analysis of their imaginary gas, providing laughs and absurd fun. This skill promises daily doses of jokes, sarcasm, and lighthearted interaction for a truly amusing experience.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
